<div>Named by Newsweek as one of the ‚ÄúTop 50 People Who Matter Most on the Internet,‚Äù Aliza Sherman is a Web pioneer, online marketing expert, published author, international speaker and regular contributor to national magazines and web sites.</div>
<div></div>
<div>Sherman is the Original Cybergirl ‚Äì a Social Media thought leader, highly sought-after online marketing expert and passionate evangelist for the Internet, particularly as a valuable and useful tool for our personal and professional lives.</div>
<div></div>
<div>She is a motivational and inspirational speaker who has been invited to speak around the world about the Internet, social media, virtual worlds, entrepreneurship and women‚Äôs empowerment.</div>
<div></div>
<div>She is the author of 7 books including Streetwise Ecommerce, The Everything Blogging Book and PowerTools for Women in Business.</div>
<div></div>
<div>Aliza Sherman is a <a href="http://www.macmillanspeakers.com/topic/Business">business keynote speaker</a> and is also booked as a <a href="http://macmillanspeakers.com/topic/Communication">professional speaker on communications</a>, specifically the fast-changing world of social media. See also our other <a href="http://macmillanspeakers.com/topic/WomensInterest">womens interests keynote speakers</a>.</div>
</div>
