rtzberg is the co-author of the best-selling <em>Artisan Bread in Five Minutes a Day, Healthy Bread in Five Minutes a Day,¬†</em>and <em>Pizza and Flatbread in Five Minutes a Day </em>with chef Zo√´ Francois.¬†He is also a physician with 20 years of experience in health care as a practitioner, consultant, and medical school professor.¬† Hertzberg's dual interest in baking and preventive health sparked a quest to adapt the techniques<em> </em>of <em>Artisan Bread in Five Minutes a Day</em> for healthier ingredients in <em>Healthy Bread in Five Minutes a Day.¬† </em>He is a dynamic speaker who travels extensively on the lecture circuit to disseminate novel approaches to health improvement, in addition to teaching super-fast bread baking in cooking schools and on television.¬† He lives in Minneapolis with his wife and two daughters.";s:10:"post_title";s:18:"Jeff Hertzberg, MD";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:17:"jeff-hertzberg-md";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2013-06-24 09:50:42";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2013-06-24 13:50:42";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:62:"http://localhost/macmillian_site/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=290";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:7:"speaker";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:119;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"446";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"4";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2012-11-14 04:20:20";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2012-11-14 04:20:20";s:12:"post_content";s:1886:"<div id="ctl00_cphMainContent_divSpeakerDesc">
