The Duke and Duchess divorced in 1996 and the couple is frequently cited as a model for civilized divorce and successful co-parenting.

For the past 12 years Sarah Ferguson, The Duchess of York, has successfully balanced motherhood, health advocacy and charity work, with a diverse and challenging international career.";s:10:"post_title";s:34:"Sarah Ferguson The Duchess of York";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:34:"sarah-ferguson-the-duchess-of-york";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2012-11-13 15:50:49";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2012-11-13 15:50:49";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:62:"http://localhost/macmillian_site/?post_type=speaker&#038;p=228";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:7:"speaker";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:227;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"392";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"4";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2012-11-14 03:12:07";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2012-11-14 03:12:07";s:12:"post_content";s:2439:"<div id="ctl00_cphMainContent_divSpeakerDesc">
