Hirshman‚Äôs first book, ‚ÄúDoes This Make My Assets Look Fat? A Woman‚Äôs Guide to Finding Financial Empowerment and Success‚Äù (SMP, 2010) suggests that many dieting rules can be applied to wealth management. Her second book, ‚ÄúI Want a Fat Asset: How to Achieve Financial Success‚Äù will be published by St. Martin‚Äôs Press this September.

